strings.Value: {n}Cephal's magic carries his voice to your ears.{/n} "I fear I have overestimated the stability of vaults... Oh, what point is making excuses! â€“ I overestimated myself. I am sorry, my friend. I let you down. You will have to go on without me."

"I will return to Varnhold for reinforcements at once. We will try to dig out the passage. But don't wait for us. Keep going, to the very depths! Find out what secrets this dungeon stores! Perhaps at the bottom you will find the key to saving all of us!"
"Good luck. But not good-bye. So long!"
